{"tid":2214474,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"如果我碌鳩想見紅","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T04:39:02.000Z","uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02f0948f68242b51ac10eac0db7824ac20fbf04f","tid":2214474,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"何以食嘅女偏很懵<br />\n自細食過多少美洞<br />\n姐姐的美味<br />\n連雞要喊窮心也痛<br />\n雞也要來竉愛<br />\n令我射精蟲<br />\n<br />\n經已明白<br />\n屎眼那洞 要塞蔥～<br />\n<br />\n曾經試過 我某夜叫雞<br />\n你曾話我窮<br />\n事實根本只有你是淫窿<br />\n做到射$3000也未懂得叫攰<br />\n黎再多一次未抖氣<br />\n做人做狗滋味<br />\n如今也記起<br />\n想一想我實情不只一個要去叫雙飛～"},{"pid":"594ddcac90bbfa389287fdacf7e2230026e414d6","tid":2214474,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5781d9729053adca085fd88b597a56370753474f","tid":2214474,"uid":366815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"又幾啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa3fef049bcffd0e818743ffb62d012e747dd95","tid":2214474,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5781d9729053adca085fd88b597a56370753474f","tid":2214474,"uid":366815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"又幾啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"知音人<br />\n你知係咩歌？"},{"pid":"0f27a6f77748013ed15019a97f2259c5cbb8a763","tid":2214474,"uid":366815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"何以待你好偏不懂～"},{"pid":"3430b8a3df35a83982d833ecd9e033ebf3e96029","tid":2214474,"uid":366815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa3fef049bcffd0e818743ffb62d012e747dd95","tid":2214474,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5781d9729053adca085fd88b597a56370753474f","tid":2214474,"uid":36